<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>742</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ a wǒ gǎn xiè nǐ tí míng hū zhào wǒ.
 jiǎo bù yǐn dǎo wǒ, cí ài huán rào wǒ.
 liè guó yǐ rèn shì nǐ, yě ràng wǒ xiǎo dé
 wàn wù de jié jú jìn le. nǐ yào shěn pàn wàn guó,
 yào duì zhǎng jiāng shuō, yào duì huáng hé shuō,
 yǐ yé hé huá wèi shén de, nà guó shì yǒu fú de guó.
 yóu zi zǒng shì cháng xiǎng niàn gù xiāng,
 zhǎng jiāng a huáng hé a, nǐ yǒu méi yǒu xiǎng guò?
 zhǎng jiāng a huáng hé a, nǐ yǒu méi yǒu xiǎng guò?</lyrics>
<title>zhǔ a wǒ gǎn xiè nǐ 迦南742</title>
</song>